About Kanguwala

According to Census 2011 information the location code or village code of Kanguwala village is 057002. Kanguwala village is located in Kalka tehsil of Panchkula district in Haryana, India. It is situated 2km away from sub-district headquarter Kalka (tehsildar office) and 17km away from district headquarter Panchkula.

The total geographical area of village is 74 hectares. Kanguwala has a total population of 571 peoples, out of which male population is 296 while female population is 275. Literacy rate of kanguwala village is 79.16% out of which 84.46% males and 73.45% females are literate. There are about 113 houses in kanguwala village. Pincode of kanguwala village locality is 134203.

Kalka is nearest town to kanguwala village for all major economic activities.
